room_title: Escape room "Save the Fleet" by Escape U in St. Augustine
room_description: Hurricane San Zenon has formed and is making its way across Florida and off the coast of St. Augustine. Your team of sailors is ordered to find some way to guide the shipping fleet to safety. Through driving rain and hammering waves you manage to make landfall just steps from the famed St. Augustine lighthouse. Now hundreds of sailors depend on your quick thinking and puzzle-solving skills as you make your way to the top and operate the life-saving beacon.
